works.description: No matter how much equipment is shoehorned into a cabin, or how much power an engine offers, there is always room for more. Earlier, we have seen some of the most incredible bling-bling vehicles and gold plated cars in the gold rush of luxury. While the Swarovski-studded Mini Cooper S by designer Marco Mehn was more a work of art than a car, the Royal MINI Cooper by Bling My Thing is something that will make every bling lover go mum. In celebration of the Royal Wedding Berlin-based company has teamed up with Swarovski to festoon a Mini Cooper with more than 300,000 Swarovski touches applied by hand.
